title: Full press conference on Kim Jong-nam's autopsy report by Health D-G
text: Tuesday, 21 February 2017 | MYT 5:51 PM Full press conference on Kim Jong-nam's autopsy report by Health D-G 86 views Health Director-General Datuk Dr Noor Hisham Abdullah gave a press conference on the autopsy report of murdered North Korean Kim Jong-nam on Tuesday. He said second autopsy was not performed on the body of Jong-nam, and the analysis on the post-mortem examination to confirm the identity of the deceased and the cause of death was still pending.
